/**
 * @file
 * Jalvarez_site module bootstrap.
 *
 * Hook implementations live in src/Hook/ as classes with the #[Hook]
 * attribute (Drupal 11 OOP hooks). Supporting services live in src/Seo/.
 *
 * - PageAttachmentsHook ......... force-attach byte/global on canvas_page
 *                                 + delegate SEO head injection
 * - MetatagsHook ................ backfill title/description for project + note
 * - CanvasPageHook .............. defensive guard for the Canvas 1.3.x
 *                                 translation-wipe bug (presave)
 * - PathautoHook ................ rewrite EN alias prefixes
 *                                 (proyectos→projects, notas→notes)
 * - Seo\SeoResolver ............. extracts SEO payload from a route
 * - Seo\SeoRenderer ............. builds meta + hreflang + JSON-LD attachments
 */
